{"tid":2102072,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"你不說……我，你說了……我 - 蔣芸","createTime":"2020-07-10T08:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T08:15:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4e16894960635545452a46e801128443b78a88","tid":2102072,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E8%94%A3%E8%8A%B8/daily/article/20200710/20952709/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E8%2594%25A3%25E8%258A%25B8%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200710%2F20952709%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=af390d8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E8%2594%25A3%25E8%258A%25B8%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200710%2F20952709%2F&h=d50bec34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E8%94%A3%E8%8A%B8/daily/article/20200710/20952709/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n你不說&hellip;&hellip;我，你說了&hellip;&hellip;我 - 蔣芸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200710/large/1594290395_f72f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200710%2Flarge%2F1594290395_f72f.jpg&h=3797034e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你不說我不明白，你說了我更不懂&hellip;&hellip;。這心情是如今大部份香港人在迷糊不解處境時的心情。<br />\n<br />\n抗拒？抗拒得了嗎？了解？如何去了解？最近頻頻跳出來的那位，以前認為掃把頭已是人中極鳳了；現在真的要對她說一聲抱歉，起碼她說瞎話時還會眼眨眨，如今這一位司級「釋法」者，說起話來那種得戚狀亢奮狀，令人百思不得其解。<br />\n<br />\n香港一向健全的法律制度下，你的官位不就是No.1嗎？而今這國安法殺到埋來，省略了正常立法程序，等於未經十月懷胎而生出來的畸形兒，一誕生就充滿了肅殺之氣，在執行層面上更是沒有律師、沒有大律師、沒有保釋、沒有陪審團，凡涉及國安法，秘密審訊更是必然的一招。<br />\n<br />\n舉世嘩然，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n地位被暗降到如今只餘一個國安法推銷員的角色。<br />\n<br />\n這幾天，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n試問如何能照單全收？<br />\n<br />\n瀰漫於我們周邊的氣氛才是最可怕的，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n你那有希望翻身解套？<br />\n<br />\n所以再多的律法專家，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n你不明我不明大家都不明。 <br />\n<br />\n蔣芸<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"3564ed6574f97d274bec15dd4ced9f19e5025946","tid":2102072,"uid":137015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:15:07.000Z","msg":"睇錯以為Ann姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}